      "acceptanceCriteria": "Version-controlled solver with documented regression test suite covering all active modules; independent code review completed.",
      "rationale": "SQA documentation covers basic version control and unit tests but lacks independent review and full regression coverage required at MRL 5. Achieved level 2 against required level 4."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
