      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative agreement metric applied to hemolysis index with uncertainty bands; systematic bias characterized across operating points.",
      "rationale": "Qualitative trend agreement demonstrated; quantitative bias and uncertainty-weighted comparison not completed for hemolysis index across full flow-speed matrix. Achieved level 3 against required level 5."
    },
